# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Local Development Environment Variables (for `pnpm dev`)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Copy this file to .env.local and adjust values as needed

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# API Configuration (optional - defaults to relative URLs)
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Uncomment to point to a specific API endpoint
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:4000

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Developer Options
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Show developer control panel at the bottom of the app
# Set to "true" to enable (default: false)
SHOW_DEV_OPTIONS=true

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Notes:
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# - NEXT_PUBLIC_* variables are embedded at build time (for `pnpm dev`)
# - SHOW_DEV_OPTIONS (no prefix) is read at runtime server-side (for Docker)
# - Both are supported for maximum flexibility across dev environments
